        public void configureAnalysis(String containerName,
                              boolean newAnalysis,
                              String aName,
                              Map<String,String> questionsToAdd,

                              @Nullable
                              Boolean suggested)
        Create, update, or truncate an analysis with provided questions or and/or question names
        Parameters:
        containerName - The container in which the analysis resides
        newAnalysis - Whether or not to create a new analysis. Incompatible with delQuestionsStr.
        aName - The name of the analysis
        questionsToAdd - The questions to be added to or initially populate the analysis.
        questionsToDelete - A list of question names to be deleted from the analysis. Incompatible with newAnalysis.
        suggested - An optional Boolean indicating whether analysis is suggested (default: false).

        Upload a new environment to an existing testrig.
        Parameters:
        containerName - The container in which the testrig resides
        testrigName - The testrig in which the (optional base environment and) new environment reside

      • getQuestionSettings

        @Nullable
public String getQuestionSettings(String network,
                                            String questionClass,
                                            List<String> components)
                                     throws IOException
        Return the JSON-serialized settings for the specified question class for the specified network; or null if either no custom settings exist for the question or no value is present at the path produced from the sepcified components.
        Parameters:
        network - The name of the network
        questionClass - The fully-qualified class name of the question
        components - The components to traverse from the root of the question settings to reach the desired section or value
        Throws:
        IOException - if there is an error reading the settings

      • writeQuestionSettings

        public void writeQuestionSettings(String network,
                                  String questionClass,
                                  List<String> components,
                                  com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode value)
                           throws IOException
        Write the JSON settings for the specified question class for the specified network at the end of the path computed from the specified components. Any absent components will be created.
        Parameters:
        network - The name of the network
        questionClass - The fully-qualified class name of the question
        components - The components to traverse from the root of the question settings to reach the desired section or value
        value - The settings value to write at the end of the path
        Throws:
        IOException - if there is an error writing the settings
